'''Imperial Prefects''' were officials in the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] that served as a liaison to [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] settlements.

==History==
Prefect [[Eugene Talmont]] wore the insignia of an [[Admiral/Legends|admiral]].

During [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], [[Mosh Barris/Legends|Mosh Barris]] worked on [[Garqi/Legends|Garqi]] as an Imperial Prefect.<ref name="Missed Chance">{{JournalCite|7|Missed Chance}}</ref>

Most prefects were in charge of [[IM-455 modular garrison|prefabricated garrison bases]].

